{"tid":2331733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷倡海外港人建黃色香港海外網絡 《人民日報》：離港者沒有好下場","createTime":"2020-12-19T04:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T05:52:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"351132c40216d39b5ed844ee82d3fa92b0c6da10","tid":2331733,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"不少港人都在考慮移民問題，佔中三子之一的前港大法律系副教授戴耀廷，日前撰文建議離開香港的港人建立起「黃色香港海外網絡」，目的不單止建立起避風港，更要讓世界聽得更清楚香港的故事。而內地官媒《人民日報》就發表評論文章，點名斥責戴耀廷的「陰謀」是「拉人入伙、騙人入坑」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/TUA3TO44KFFJNKEJQZLEPQHHAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2FTUA3TO44KFFJNKEJQZLEPQHHAM%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=fc88c1ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2FTUA3TO44KFFJNKEJQZLEPQHHAM%2F&h=9a465a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/TUA3TO44KFFJNKEJQZLEPQHHAM/</a>"},{"pid":"3d7491ab015258a0ba0146cf8c043211766188ae","tid":2331733,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95b52d91ae78ea181e7c7e07c5788afd38b1b09b","tid":2331733,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"海外黃圈呢啲嘢洗撚戴要停呢條柒頭講咩，上年已經話要海外黃圈啦，宜家係要擴大全球茶聯，唔好再淨係玩twitter ，人哋习子兵法教我哋要全民統戰，重視考古香港五萬年歷史文化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}